    "SUMMARY": "Kevin Daniel Van Den Kerkhof Guitoun (Arabic: كيفن دانيال فان دين كيرخوف ڨيطون; born 14 March 1996), called Kevin Guitoun in Algeria, is a professional footballer who plays as a right-back for  Ligue 2 club Metz. Born in France, he plays for the Algeria national team."
